red color     ===> if a new file created or existed file modified this is known as working
command : git add .


green color    ===> staging

git status ===> to know the file status

git add filename ====> wriking to staging

git reset filename ====> staging to working

git commit ====> commited stage
empty



1) git init ===> For new repository (Created in local it means our machine)
2) How to push changes to remote from local  
	stages = working => staged => commited stage ==> push
